#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-06-04-chatgpt-project-workflow.rst:63
msgid ""
"ChatGPT が参照できる情報源は **(1) チャット履歴** ・ **(2) アップロードファイル** ・ **(3) 明示的に読み込ませた "
"URL** の三つだけ。 規模が膨らむほど **“与え方”** が重要になります。"
msgstr ""
"There are only three sources of information that ChatGPT can reference: "
"**(1) Chat history**, **(2) Upload files**, and **(3) URLs that are "
"explicitly loaded**. As the scale expands, **“how to give”** becomes more "
"important."

